# Brake Repair in Missoula, MT

Your brake system is the most safety-critical system on your vehicle, and when something feels off — a noise, a soft pedal, a pull to one side — it's worth understanding what's actually happening before assuming the worst or ignoring it. This page explains what brake repair involves, what causes brake problems, and how we diagnose them before recommending any work.

---

## What This Service Covers

- Inspection and replacement of brake pads and shoes
- Rotor resurfacing or replacement (front and rear)
- Brake caliper service, including slide pin cleaning and replacement
- Brake fluid flush and hydraulic system inspection
- Brake hose and hard line inspection for leaks or deterioration
- ABS system diagnosis when warning lights are present

